            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日本股市轉跌，日經平均指數上午收市報56790點，跌151點，跌幅0.27%。</p>\n</div>",
